### Read Operations

### GET all products
GET http://localhost:3000/products

### GET product by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/products/1

### GET product by non-existent ID
GET http://localhost:3000/products/999

### GET products by category
GET http://localhost:3000/products/category/Electronics

### Search by keyword (phone)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/search?keyword=phone

### Search by keyword (s)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/search?keyword=s


### Update & Toggle

### Partial update (PATCH)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/products/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 899.99,
    "stock": 45
}

### Validation error: Empty name
PATCH http://localhost:3000/products/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": ""
}

### Full replacement (PUT)
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
    "price": 1099.99,
    "stock": 30,
    "category": "Electronics"
}

### Validation error: Missing required fields for PUT
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 799.99
}

### Toggle status (True -> False)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/products/2/toggle

### Toggle status (False -> True)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/products/2/toggle


### Delete Operations

### DELETE product
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/4

### DELETE already deleted product (404)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/4

### Verify 3 products remain
GET http://localhost:3000/products


### Validation Errors

### POST missing name
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 999.99,
    "stock": 50,
    "category": "Electronics"
}

### POST negative price
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Invalid Product",
    "price": -5,
    "stock": 50,
    "category": "Electronics"
}

### POST with unknown field
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Unknown Field Product",
    "price": 100,
    "category": "Electronics",
    "extraField": "Something"
}

### POST with no body
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Content-Type: application/json

{}